Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們成為神樹大人的勇者後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,已經過了一個半月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在神樹大人製造的防禦結界樹海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,迎擊人類的敵人宿命點是勇者的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,根據風前輩所說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,宿命點共有12隻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,全部幹掉任務就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要加油才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是第5隻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點 在這裡迎擊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟空了一個月 能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,把這裡這樣這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,車到山前多半有路啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別說廢話 好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是… 是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.71,0:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,輕鬆愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,封印開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你見識下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子要自己動手？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這… 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這種煙霧彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你的氣息暴露啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,殲~ 滅~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,諸行無常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一個個都呆呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這種人會是神樹大人選出的勇者？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼 小豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是三好夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大赦派遣來的如假包換的正式勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說 你們下崗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好 辛苦啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,====================Title====================
